Carlos Becerra (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carlos_Becerra_(actor) 0 Carlos Becerra (born July 12, 1991), is an American actor, producer and entrepreneur. Becerra debuted as the host of Discovery Channel TV series Carspotting. Carlos_Becerra ( born July_12_,_1991 ) , is an_American_actor_,_producer_and_entrepreneur .
